'''博克多汗冬宮'''（Bogd Khan Palace Museum、{{lang-mn|Богд Хааны Ордон}}）位於[[烏蘭巴托|烏蘭巴托]]南部，現爲博物館。這座宮殿是[[第八世哲布尊丹巴呼圖克圖|第八世]][[哲布尊丹巴呼图克图|哲布尊丹巴呼图克图]][[第八世哲布尊丹巴呼圖克圖|博克多汗]]的四個住所中唯一仍存在的<ref name="地球の歩き方">{{Cite book|year=2007|title=[[地球の歩き方|地球の歩き方]]モンゴル 2007-2008年版|volume=|publisher=[[ダイヤモンド社|ダイヤモンド社]]|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mongoliantemples.net/images/pdfs/OLDUBWEB%202008.pdf |title=Monasteries and Temples of Bogdiin Khьree, Ikh Khьree or Urga, the Old Capital City of Mongolia in the First Part of the Twentieth Century |accessdate=January 30, 2009 |author= |last=Majer |first=Zsuzsa |authorlink= |coauthors=Teleki, Krisztina |date= |year= |month= |format= |work= |publisher=Documentation of Mongolian Monasteries |location=Budapest |pages=36 |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227184244/http://www.mongoliantemples.net/images/pdfs/OLDUBWEB%202008.pdf |archivedate=2009-02-27 |quote= |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。另外三座宮殿分別為[[东库伦|東庫倫]]的黃宮、白宮及潘德林，另有紅宮（{{lang-mn|Улаан ордон}}或Хайстайн лаврин，Khastain Laurin ）尚存部分建築於{{Translink|mn|Удирдлагын академи|4=National Academy of Governance}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Түүх түүхээрээ үлдэнэ|url=https://www.barilga.mn/n/4457/|access-date=2021-10-18|work=Barilga.MN - Барилгын нэгдсэн портал|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020105604/https://www.barilga.mn/n/4457/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Богд Хааны Хастайн лавиран буюу Хүрэн ордонг Богд хааны ордон музейд шилжүүлэх хүсэлтэй байна|url=http://www.mnb.mn/i/2867|access-date=2021-10-18|date=2013-07-25|work=mnb.mn|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020150140/http://www.mnb.mn/i/2867|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Bogd Khan's Red Palace and its Contested History exhibition to take place|url=https://montsame.mn/en/read/130082|access-date=2021-10-18|work=MONTSAME News Agency|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/2